        <type>int</type>
        <definition>int bt_mesh_light_ctrl_srv_on</definition>
        <argsstring>(struct bt_mesh_light_ctrl_srv *srv)</argsstring>
        <name>bt_mesh_light_ctrl_srv_on</name>
        <param>
          <type>struct <ref refid="structbt__mesh__light__ctrl__srv" kindref="compound">bt_mesh_light_ctrl_srv</ref> *</type>
          <declname>srv</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Turn the light on. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Instructs the controlled Lightness Server to turn the light on. If the light was already on, the dimming timeout is reset. If the light was in the Prolong state, it&apos;s moved back into the On state.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">srv</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Light Lightness Control Server instance.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<parameterlist kind="retval"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>0</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The Light Lightness Control Server was successfully turned on. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>-EBUSY</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The Light Lightness Control Server is disabled. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
